Privacy Policy

Namaz Vakti: Adhan & Dhikr

Last updated: May 21, 2026

This Privacy Policy explains how ARON LABS collects, uses, and protects information when you use the “Namaz Vakti: Adhan & Dhikr” mobile application.

By using the application, you agree to this Privacy Policy.

1. Information We Collect
Location Information

The app may access your device’s approximate or precise location in order to provide accurate prayer times based on your region.

Location data:

Is used only for prayer time calculations
Is not continuously tracked
Is not sold or shared with third parties
Notification Permission

The app may request notification permission in order to send:

Adhan notifications
Prayer reminders
Daily Dhikr reminders
Device Information

Anonymous technical information may be collected to improve app performance and stability, including:

Device model
Operating system version
Crash logs
App version

This information does not personally identify users.

2. Information We Do Not Collect

The app does not collect:

Full name or personal identity information
National ID numbers
Credit card or payment information
Contacts, messages, or photos
3. Advertising Services

The app may use third-party advertising services. These services may process device information for ad delivery and analytics purposes.

Services used:

